---
title: One Pot Creamy Chicken Pasta with Mushrooms, Leeks and Parsley
description: Rich, creamy and bursting with fresh flavours, our one pot creamy chicken pasta is a no-fuss dish with minimal washing up.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pot-creamy-chicken-pasta-0b9c554f-3484d393.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/one-pot-creamy-chicken-pasta-5dfbb3ae13376732637996a4-da3a6920.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/one-pot-creamy-chicken-pasta-5dfbb3ae13376732637996a4
servings: 2
time required: 20 minutes
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
cuisine: European
nutrition:
  calories: 762 kcal
